{"name":"Immune Suppression","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.emMU9jJhbTuPWRss]{Instinctual Suppression} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.6oYdY9WNPVqldAr5]{Resistant Suppression}</p><p>When you use your Suppress, choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, force, lightning, necrotic, poison, psychic, radiant, or thunder. You gain immunity to the chosen damage type until the Suppress ends or you use your Suppress again.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-wall-flame-ring-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hvSc3MPZjy4v9KaE"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811927346,"modifiedTime":1674813235731,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"1NCuSoaO80cLjK16"}
{"name":"Crippling Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.y7eD8cy1hmZgE8Qk]{Enervating Jinx} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.OulSr1GPhsibyjhz]{Startling Jinx}</p><p>The following jinxes are added to the list of options you can choose when a creature fails its Wisdom saving throw against your Jinx feature:</p><ul><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next attack roll it makes.</p></li><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next saving throw it makes. Once you use this jinx on a creature, you must finish a long rest before you can use it on that creature again.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-spiral-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ETAOKisL4m53Au0E"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674810707922,"modifiedTime":1674813152247,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"23SXY91z4aA388ye"}
{"name":"Explosive Bane","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.RL7ySWefc3GDUSBs]{Eldritch Bane} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.DuW42aGsi9NLFLKc]{Martial Bane}</p><p>Once during each of your turns when you hit a creature with an attack or deal damage to it with an accursed spell, you can cause the target to take an additional 1d8 necrotic damage from the attack or spell. When you use this ability, you can also choose to expend a spell slot to cause the creature to take an additional 1d8 necrotic damage per level of the expended spell slot.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-blade-hooked-orange-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7wMr2jhyIZ2tgEd6"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811610679,"modifiedTime":1674813203701,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"2S6mAf98oNULOzvK"}
{"name":"Sleighting Imprecation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.DJ0VbPAKB4FKiLqp]{Enshrouding Imprecation}</p><p>While you’re in dim light or darkness, you can ignore the somatic components of your accursed spells, you gain a bonus to Dexterity (Sleight of Hand) and Dexterity (Thieves’ Tools) checks equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum +1) , and you can magically form the magicks of your curse into a set of thieves’ tools whenever you would make an ability check using thieves’ tools.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/hand-eye-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xHFxlRasMHLZvbv7"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809687466,"modifiedTime":1674810424029,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5xStL1jkpH0s5uYm"}
{"name":"Resistant Suppression","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.7qx0UlxvV9qkrRlg]{Bolstering Suppression}</p><p>When you use your Suppress, you gain resistance to any damage type of your choice. You lose this resistance when the Suppress ends or you use your Suppress again.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-blue-purple.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TRPC5og3PF27noJB"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809428684,"modifiedTime":1674810402291,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"6oYdY9WNPVqldAr5"}
{"name":"Hex Aura","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level,@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.9tGhpj35N3dlrx5o]{Hex Armor}</p><p>When a creature you can see within 30 feet of you causes you to take damage, you can use your reaction to cast hex on that creature, without expending a spell slot. When you cast the spell with this ability, it ends early if the target drops to 0 hit points.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.C2sR0kbeVkA6xEbz"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808776453,"modifiedTime":1674810350172,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"77C0G2CtkzJ8oGrV"}
{"name":"Bolstering Suppression","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse protects you when you give it a nudge. When you use your Suppress, you gain temporary hit points equal to your accursed level + your curse ability modifier. You lose any remaining temporary hit points from this ability when the Suppress ends.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.accursed.levels + @abilities.int.mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-deflect-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KcDOubRzK2snSWkT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674804796671,"modifiedTime":1674808150621,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"7qx0UlxvV9qkrRlg"}
{"name":"Hex Armor","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you’re in danger, the magicks of your curse manifest around you like a suit of armor. Your AC can’t be less than 13 + your curse ability modifier, regardless of what kind of armor you’re wearing.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-glowing-triangle-purple-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tDTnGYQLVHRbhsGU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674807282315,"modifiedTime":1674808804691,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"9tGhpj35N3dlrx5o"}
{"name":"Negating Anathema","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.mMA8uyO7G3OMEhqz]{Capacious Anathema} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.TOyctVHDb4mM3qfa]{Obstinate Anathema}</p><p>When you become the target of a spell, you can use your reaction to attempt to negate the spell’s effects on yourself. If the spell is of 5th level or lower, the spell fails to affect you. If the spell is of 6th level or higher, you must make a curse ability check with DC equal to 15 + the spell’s level; on a success, the spell fails to affect you. You must be able to see the source of the spell to use this ability, and this ability has no effect on the spell’s other targets.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lKxbKKpHHFmvsQAU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812134518,"modifiedTime":1674813253459,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"9zh6yIEmJb1xeAUq"}
{"name":"Afflict","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As an action, you can expend a spell slot to attempt to afflict a creature within 30 feet that you can see with your choice of one of your curse’s ailments. The creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or suffer the chosen ailment for the duration. At the end of each of an afflicted creature’s turns, it can repeat the saving throw, ending its affliction on a successful save. A @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.15Fa6q1nH27XfbR8]{dispel magic}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.WzvJ7G3cqvIubsLk]{greater restoration}, or @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.XZhdgVK3cLoxNCQl]{remove curse} spell cast on the target also ends its affliction.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-chains-orb-movement-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5To38ahAb5xCZIwC"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674802307123,"modifiedTime":1674802380343,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"B7zo4IlA8zKpaEId"}
{"name":"Enshrouding Imprecation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse’s magicks coat you like a shadowy cloak. You can Hide as a bonus action on your turn. Additionally, while you’re in dim light or darkness, you can attempt to hide even from a creature that can see you.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/shadow-stealth-eyes-purple.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.YBXMvp2TVbZoDIsg"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674806621190,"modifiedTime":1674808151990,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"DJ0VbPAKB4FKiLqp"}
{"name":"Martial Bane","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.Y7k2VZ9C90Qs03Uj]{Hostile Bane}</p><p>You lose the benefits of your Hostile Bane. Instead, each time you hit a creature with a weapon attack on your turn, you can cause the attack to deal additional necrotic damage equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum 1).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/hand-claw-glow-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DV3r2Ffi5Yvkf8dq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809209548,"modifiedTime":1674810377528,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"DuW42aGsi9NLFLKc"}
{"name":"Scourge Visage","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.Kq1v3Px6JexHf2eL]{Scourge Speech}</p><p>As an action, you can cause the magicks of your curse to manifest around you as a horrifying visage. The visage intangibly coats your entire body and anything you’re wearing or carrying, and can look like a cloak, a suit of armor, or another type of inanimate covering that obscures your features. </p><p>While you’re cloaked in the visage, ability checks made to ascertain your emotional state or whether you’re lying automatically fail, and whenever an enemy within 5 feet of you that can see you makes a saving throw against being frightened, it subtracts your curse ability modifier (minimum 1) from the roll.</p><p>The visage remains until you become incapacitated or you choose to dismiss it (no action required).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-glow.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9fF3CWKUpDbihmOW"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809585579,"modifiedTime":1674810418059,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"K5bz4JNuypbxrdVW"}
{"name":"Hex Phalanx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.77C0G2CtkzJ8oGrV]{Hex Aura} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.QO1BqfrqMdwY0aMx]{Hex Plate}</p><p>Your curse recognizes your allies and will protect them while they are alongside you. As long as one or more friendly creatures are within 5 feet of you, each of those creatures gains a bonus to its AC, and you and each of those creatures gains a bonus to any Strength or Dexterity saving throw it makes. The bonus is equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum +1). You and at least one friendly creature within 5 feet of you must be conscious to gain the bonus.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-purple-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UYiFWkqQBtlRab8r"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811726801,"modifiedTime":1674813215053,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"K9cEYOKZ4pjMlRhv"}
{"name":"Scourge Speech","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you speak, you can imbue your voice with the power and vile nature of your curse, causing it to boom up to three times as loud as normal. Additionally, whenever you make a Charisma (Intimidation) or Charisma (Persuasion) check, you can gain a bonus to the check equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum +1). When you use either of these abilities, your voice gains an unsettling supernatural quality.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/sonic/scream-wail-shout-teal.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mxrLu9MfIMUWgvAR"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808001255,"modifiedTime":1674808155468,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Kq1v3Px6JexHf2eL"}
{"name":"Vengeful Bane","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.RL7ySWefc3GDUSBs]{Eldritch Bane} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.DuW42aGsi9NLFLKc]{Martial Bane}</p><p>When a creature you can see within 30 feet of you causes you to take damage, you can use your reaction to make a weapon attack against that creature or cast an accursed spell at the creature, given that the creature is within range. The spell must have a casting time of 1 action and target only that creature. If the creature would take damage from the attack or spell, it takes additional necrotic damage equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum 1).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/shield-damaged-broken-gold.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WJlRVun7Ty9Tbbi6"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812617407,"modifiedTime":1674813293257,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MAfDqUdlCWVYdV0Q"}
{"name":"Swift Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse excitedly responds to being used for jinxes. You can use your Jinx as a bonus action. When you do, you can’t use your action to maintain the jinx on your subsequent turns, even if the creature hasn’t made the associated type of roll.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-snare-brown.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.htTjWy1zftUhIkmB"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808079909,"modifiedTime":1674808757064,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"NwtyvmNF4XmW93Jg"}
{"name":"Dispelling Anathema","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.mMA8uyO7G3OMEhqz]{Capacious Anathema} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.TOyctVHDb4mM3qfa]{Obstinate Anathema}</p><p>You learn the @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.uah-spells.LpEHqFsUfPoyEWdy]{Dispel Caster} spell f you don’t already know it. It doesn’t count against the number of accursed spells you know. You can cast dispel caster once, without expending a spell slot. When you do, you must finish a long rest before you can cast it with this ability again.</p><p>Additionally, when you make an ability check as part of your Arcane Anathema, you add your proficiency bonus to that ability check.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/magical/construct-golem-stone-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KS9lYQ6vnrlWb6Wq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674810825918,"modifiedTime":1674813179258,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OGrCLrCw04Pg3Yz5"}
{"name":"Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As an action, you can attempt to bestow a minor curse on a creature you can see within 30 feet of you. That creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become subject to your choice of one of the following jinxes until the end of your next turn:</p><ul><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next ability check it makes.</p></li><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next attack roll it makes against a creature of your choice that you can see.</p></li></ul><p>If a creature can see you when you use this feature, it knows that you are the source of the jinx. Until the target makes the type of roll associated with the jinx, you can use your action on subsequent turns to maintain the effect, extending the jinx’s duration until the end of your next turn. However, the jinx ends once the target makes the associated type of roll, if you are more than 90 feet from the target, or if any of the @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.15Fa6q1nH27XfbR8]{Dispel Magic}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.WzvJ7G3cqvIubsLk]{Greater Restoration}, or @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.XZhdgVK3cLoxNCQl]{Remove Curse} spells is cast on the target.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kE7bJHEC9LoqakuC"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674800143416,"modifiedTime":1674801930780,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OO126tlUUYZdY4TX"}
{"name":"Supress","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a bonus action, you can expend a spell slot and choose any number of your curse’s ailments. You ignore the effects of the chosen ailments for the duration.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-chains-ropes-purple.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.frAguwTbrv1ycUZA"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674803040686,"modifiedTime":1674803113933,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OQSxgGu4EW5xlmhK"}
{"name":"Jealous Blight","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, your curse begins possessively guarding you from others of its ilk, refusing to share its host. When you touch or attune to a cursed object other than your curse, it doesn’t stop being cursed, but the object’s curse doesn’t affect you.</p><p>Once you reach 7th level in this class, your curse protects you from a wider range of effects. You are immune to curse effects other than your curse, such as the hex and bestow curse spells, and your hit point maximum and ability scores can’t be reduced against your will.</p><p>Once you reach 14th level in this class, a magical effect other than your curse can’t age you, possess you, put you to sleep, or transform you against your will. Once you reach 20th level in this class, a magical effect other than your curse can’t impose disadvantage on any roll you make.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-blades-teal.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uFzGelclJgE8roKo"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674801455627,"modifiedTime":1674813450592,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OlJizxp5lAFcMfZZ"}
{"name":"Startling Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The following jinxes are added to the list of options you can choose when a creature fails its Wisdom saving throw against your Jinx feature:</p><ul><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next saving throw it makes against being frightened.</p></li><li><p>The target has disadvantage on the next Constitution saving throw it makes to maintain its concentration.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-yellow.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.87Rihv82N2WLngQL"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809860997,"modifiedTime":1674810429337,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OulSr1GPhsibyjhz"}
{"name":"Scourge Presence","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.tNEu8BJfuWzjzRcw]{Scourge Sense} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.K5bz4JNuypbxrdVW]{Scourge Visage}</p><p>As a bonus action, you can force each creature of your choice that can see or hear you within 30 feet of you to make a Wisdom saving throw or become frightened of you for 1 minute. At the start of each of its turns, a creature frightened by this ability takes 2d8 psychic damage if it can see or hear you, or can repeat the saving throw if it can’t see or hear you, ending the effect on itself on a success. If a creature’s saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the creature is immune to this ability until you finish a long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-evil-horned-giant.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vzpyUe5kVnVEs7ux"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812332777,"modifiedTime":1674813267461,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"P7EOvnPkUsVQuvus"}
{"name":"Hex Plate","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level,@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.9tGhpj35N3dlrx5o]{Hex Armor}</p><p>Your AC can’t be less than 16 + your curse ability modifier, regardless of what kind of armor you’re wearing.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-pentagon-red.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kSjDXnCYuUR8I6YT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808936834,"modifiedTime":1674810357090,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"QO1BqfrqMdwY0aMx"}
{"name":"Eldritch Bane","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.Y7k2VZ9C90Qs03Uj]{Hostile Bane}</p><p>Once during each of your turns when you roll damage for an accursed class feature or accursed spell that doesn’t include an attack, you can add your curse ability modifier (minimum 1) to the damage roll.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-contained-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cMTJmFyP2SUtF6qh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808539902,"modifiedTime":1674810341549,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"RL7ySWefc3GDUSBs"}
{"name":"Scourge Attunement","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.tNEu8BJfuWzjzRcw]{Scourge Sense} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.K5bz4JNuypbxrdVW]{Scourge Visage}</p><p>You can attune to three additional magic items, provided that each of the additional items is cursed. If a cursed item you’re attuned to is a weapon or suit of armor, you are considered proficient with the item for the duration of your attunement to it.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/equipment/neck/amulet-geometric-gold-green.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.M23IkybAR8Y6FNPr"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812235294,"modifiedTime":1674813260713,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"RcVlJd0g2nzRF3a8"}
{"name":"Conquered Curse","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Through unfortunate circumstances, you were stricken with a curse that should have broken you. However, whether by sheer willpower, introspective meditation, or arcane study, you not only overcame the worst of the challenges your curse presented, but learned to harness its power. Choose the curse you conquered: Curse of Animation, Curse of the Armament, Curse of Combustion, Curse of the Created, Curse of Immortality, Curse of Misfortune, Curse of Mummification, Curse of Petrification, or Curse of Somnolence. All conquered curses are detailed at the end of the class.</p><p>Your curse has become an integral part of you. The @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.XZhdgVK3cLoxNCQl]{Remove Curse} spell, as well as any similar effect, has no effect on your curse when it is cast on you. If your curse takes the form of a magical disease, you can’t be cured of it by any means.</p><p>Your choice grants you features at 1st level, and again at 3rd, 5th, 11th, 15th, and 20th level, as well as a list of curse spells (detailed in the Spellcasting class feature).</p><h2>Ailments</h2><p>Each curse has ailments caused by its lingering effects. They are inconvenient, and occasionally dangerous, detriments to which you are always subject, and are referred to by features you gain later in this class.</p><h2>Curse Ability &amp; Curse Save DC</h2><p>Some of your accursed features require your target to make a saving throw to resist the feature’s effects. Due to the varying ways that an accursed can overcome their affliction, not all utilize the same ability score to control it. Choose Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma as your curse ability.</p><p>You should choose Intelligence if you scoured the multiverse for secrets that allow you to manage your curse using rituals or minor magical practices, Wisdom if you used introspective meditation techniques to harmonize with your curse and make it a part of you, or Charisma if you conquered your curse through sheer force of will or by bargaining with it.</p><p>Depending on the curse ability you chose, the saving throw DC of your accursed features is calculated as follows:</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Curse save DC</strong> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your curse ability modifier</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/voodoo-doll-pain-damage-red.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.LEUrtpeMsNFYw550"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674799604274,"modifiedTime":1674801927590,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"SCSk4nsWrKB2dGML"}
{"name":"Obstinate Anathema","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.zOqEwSUxQtD9oy1u]{Arcane Anathema}</p><p>When you are incapacitated, paralyzed, petrified, or stunned by a spell’s effects, you are still able to use your action, provided that you aren’t unconscious and the only action you take is to use your Arcane Anathema.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/magical/humanoid-silhouette-glowing-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.bBD02EYQjh81kF58"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809307684,"modifiedTime":1674810388930,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"TOyctVHDb4mM3qfa"}
