{"name":"Infectious Affliction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.wz9H5n7VgZhpvyBO]{Fecund Affliction}</p><p>When your affliction ends on a creature before its full duration has elapsed, you can use your reaction to attempt to afflict a different creature you can see within 30 feet of the previously afflicted creature.</p><p>The new target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become the sufferer of the affliction for its remaining duration.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/hand-light-green.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SCNVmesHA4LAjNsI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808992690,"modifiedTime":1674810362110,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"UN0sPcB5A5u8oCY2"}
{"name":"Hostile Bane","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse imbues your attacks with its dark magicks. Once during each of your turns when you hit a creature with an attack, you can cause the attack to deal additional necrotic damage equal to your curse ability modifier (minimum 1).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-blade-knife-orange-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.OHuu9TLMkpkLgwrd"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674807929989,"modifiedTime":1674811664555,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Y7k2VZ9C90Qs03Uj"}
{"name":"Vile Affliction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.UN0sPcB5A5u8oCY2]{Infectious Affliction} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.cytca5kZTBqa9vqa]{Prolific Affliction}</p><p>You can use your Afflict as a bonus action on your turn. Additionally, when you use your Afflict, you can choose any number of your ailments. If a target fails its saving throw, it suffers each of the chosen ailments for the duration.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/earth/strike-body-stone-crumble.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nrHxp7FOtFmXpWBZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812725789,"modifiedTime":1674813299424,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"a3Wsz6OmzW7zybNA"}
{"name":"Prolific Affliction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.wz9H5n7VgZhpvyBO]{Fecund Affliction}</p><p>When you spend a spell slot of 2nd-level or higher to use your Afflict, instead of increasing the affliction’s duration, you can choose an additional target for each slot level above 1st. If you do, each target that fails its saving throw is afflicted for 1 minute.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-beam-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gS1QI7jbbUbpPLcl"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809361156,"modifiedTime":1674810395775,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"cytca5kZTBqa9vqa"}
{"name":"Ailment Control","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 2nd level, you can also use your spell slots to exert control over your curse’s ailments, either afflicting another creature with one of your ailments or suppressing your ailments’ effects on yourself. The duration of the effect depends on the level of the spell slot expended to use it: 1 minute for a 1st-level spell slot, 10 minutes for a 2nd-level, 1 hour for a 3rd-level, 8 hours for a 4th-level, or 24 hours for a spell slot of 5th-level or higher.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.B7zo4IlA8zKpaEId]{Afflict}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.OQSxgGu4EW5xlmhK]{Supress}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/holy/meditation-chi-focus-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vRFKqheHZmQ1K8S8"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674801252135,"modifiedTime":1674803278404,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"diiGjf2wPSFG91zI"}
{"name":"Instinctual Suppression","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.7qx0UlxvV9qkrRlg]{Bolstering Suppression}</p><p>When you roll initiative, you can use your reaction to use your Suppress. If you do, you gain a +4 bonus to your AC until the end of your next turn. You can take this reaction even if you are surprised.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-deflect-teal.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vMBcvY4Dr1otFE69"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809129230,"modifiedTime":1674810369375,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"emMU9jJhbTuPWRss"}
{"name":"Doubling Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.y7eD8cy1hmZgE8Qk]{Enervating Jinx} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.OulSr1GPhsibyjhz]{Startling Jinx}</p><p>When you use your Jinx, you can target a second creature within range. If both targets fail their Wisdom saving throw against the feature, you can choose a different jinx for each target.</p><p>If neither jinxed target makes the associated type of roll before the end of your next turn, you can use the same action to maintain both jinxes, given that the jinx hasn’t ended for another reason and you are able to maintain the jinx.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectiles-binary-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.IvZfmssNCOqVHJU6"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811445703,"modifiedTime":1674813188347,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"fZlLl1AfqKpQ47Qg"}
{"name":"Spellcasting","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 2nd level, you learn to use your curse’s vile magicks to fuel the casting of spells. See Chapter 10 in the Player’s Handbook for the general rules of spellcasting.</p><h2>Spell Slots</h2><p>The Accursed table shows how many spell slots you have to cast your spells of 1st level and higher. To cast one of these spells, you must expend a spell slot of the spell’s level or higher. You regain all expended spell slots when you finish a long rest.</p><h2>Curse Spells</h2><p>Each Conquered Curse has a list of spells — its curse spells — that you learn when you reach certain levels in this class, as shown in the curse description. These spells are added to the accursed spell list for you and are included in the number in the Spells Known column of the Accursed table. You ignore the material component requirement of a curse spell if it has one.</p><h2>Spells Known of 1st Level and Higher</h2><p>You know the curse spell you gain at 2nd level from your Conquered Curse, and one 1st-level spell of your choice from the accursed spell list, for a total of two spells known.</p><p>The Spells Known column of the Accursed table shows when you learn more spells of your choice from the accursed spell list. Each of these spells must be of a level for which you have spell slots. For example, when you reach 5th level in this class, you learn one new spell of 1st or 2nd level, in addition to the curse spell you gain at 5th level from your Conquered Curse.</p><p>Additionally, when you gain a level in this class, you can choose one of the accursed spells you know — which can be one of your curse spells — and replace it with another spell from the accursed spell list, which must also be of a level for which you have spell slots.</p><h2>Spellcasting Ability</h2><p>Your curse ability is your spellcasting ability for your accursed spells, since your ability to cast spells comes from the control you have over your curse’s power. You use your curse ability whenever a spell refers to your spellcasting ability. In addition, you use your curse ability modifier when setting the saving throw DC for an accursed spell you cast and when making an attack roll with one.</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Spell save DC</strong> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your curse ability modifier</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Spell attack modifier</strong> = your proficiency bonus + your curse ability modifier</p><h2>Spellcasting Focus</h2><p>When you gain this feature, choose arcane foci, druidic foci, or holy symbols, depending on how you discovered to channel your curse. You can use the chosen type of implement or a cursed object as a spellcasting focus (found in chapter 5 of the Player’s Handbook) for your accursed spells.</p><h2>Accursed Spell List</h2><p>Here’s the list of spells you consult when you learn an accursed spell. The list is organized by spell level, not character level. Many of these spells are from the Player’s Handbook. If a spell’s name is followed by the XGE superscript, the spell can be found in Xanathar’s Guide to Everything. Additionally, spells with the UAH superscript are original spells that can be found in Chapter 4: Feats &amp; Spells.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-hand-gray.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SZV0TEfAjb4ucnMy"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674800494372,"modifiedTime":1674813376006,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"hWHDxIl3JQN2r1Nw"}
{"name":"Adaptive Malediction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you finish a short rest, you can choose to replace one of your other metamorphoses with a different metamorphosis, and when you finish a long rest, you can choose to replace any number of your other metamorphoses with different metamorphoses. To choose a replacement metamorphosis, you must meet its prerequisites, and it can’t have an 18th level prerequisite.</p><p>If replacing a metamorphosis causes you to no longer meet another metamorphosis’ prerequisites, you must also replace that metamorphosis. If you are replacing two or more metamorphoses simultaneously with this ability, you can choose a metamorphosis at the same time you choose its prerequisite metamorphosis.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-entangled-humanoid.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.LGOdSyjEcm8tw94v"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674810601353,"modifiedTime":1674812883329,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"kbZmu6qKTEpM73C5"}
{"name":"Capacious Anathema","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.zOqEwSUxQtD9oy1u]{Arcane Anathema}</p><p>When you use your Arcane Anathema and succeed on the ability check, you can choose up to five other creatures within 30 feet of the target that you can see that are also affected by the spell. You end the spell’s effects on each of the chosen creatures.</p><p>Once you use this ability, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-grow-shrink-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.m1Htkc0HstVAUXbI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808169692,"modifiedTime":1674810333279,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"mMA8uyO7G3OMEhqz"}
{"name":"Facile Suppression","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.emMU9jJhbTuPWRss]{Instinctual Suppression} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.6oYdY9WNPVqldAr5]{Resistant Suppression}</p><p>You can use your Suppress at will, without expending a spell slot. When you use Suppress with this ability, the Suppress doesn’t end until you die or until you choose to end it (no action required).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-chains-ropes-net-red-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wqV6knRNXpmQPX6H"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811523445,"modifiedTime":1674813197657,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"mTBHqgm67WGOeoZI"}
{"name":"Insidious Imprecation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.0tBZAWioRXe0Blk0]{Muffling Imprecation} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.5xStL1jkpH0s5uYm]{Sleighting Imprecation}</p><p>If you’re hidden from a creature when one of your accursed features or an accursed spell you cast requires the creature to make a saving throw, it has disadvantage on any saving throw it makes against the spell or feature this turn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/nature/stealth-hide-eyes-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.t2kuO422ePlp3AaM"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812022871,"modifiedTime":1674813245141,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"sNtYhFZm9Y0HLZi2"}
{"name":"Scourge Sense","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.Kq1v3Px6JexHf2eL]{Scourge Speech}</p><p>You can cast the @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Mzh95utKDPIrjiH8]{Detect Evil and Good} and @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.ghXTfe7sgCbgf1Q8]{Detect Magic} spells at will, without expending a spell slot. While you concentrate on either spell, you are also aware if any creature or object within 30 feet of you is cursed, and can use your action on your turn to learn the properties of a curse affecting one such creature or object.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/eyes/void-single-black-purple.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EtTm6zofKzZDSH1u"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674809486959,"modifiedTime":1674810411124,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"tNEu8BJfuWzjzRcw"}
{"name":"Transferring Affliction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.emMU9jJhbTuPWRss]{Instinctual Suppression} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.cytca5kZTBqa9vqa]{Prolific Affliction}</p><p>When one or more creatures fail their saving throw against your Afflict, you can choose to ignore the effects of the chosen ailment for the duration. If you do, the afflicted creature has disadvantage on saving throws it makes to end its affliction and takes 1d8 necrotic damage at the start of each of its turns for the duration.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/encase-creature-humanoid-hold.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6RQsbM2rTEVVdpnd"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812422650,"modifiedTime":1674813275819,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"u6zF9Hln6N2q7ffW"}
{"name":"Fecund Affliction","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse gleefully spreads its effects to other victims. Once, you can use your Afflict without expending a spell slot. Its duration is 1 minute. You regain the use of this ability when you finish a short or long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/hand-light-pink.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pY5VgvjskyzfQRoI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674806769317,"modifiedTime":1674808152842,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"wz9H5n7VgZhpvyBO"}
{"name":"Enervating Jinx","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 10th Level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.NwtyvmNF4XmW93Jg]{Swift Jinx}</p><p>The following jinxes are added to the list of options you can choose when a creature fails its Wisdom saving throw against your Jinx feature:</p><ul><li><p>When the target makes its next damage roll for a spell, it rolls the damage dice twice and uses the lower result.</p></li><li><p>When the target makes its next damage roll for a weapon, it rolls the damage dice twice and uses the lower result.</p></li></ul><p>You can use these jinx options a total number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain your expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-orange.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iCJCPTfbkNjTBECc"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674808627251,"modifiedTime":1674810730162,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"y7eD8cy1hmZgE8Qk"}
{"name":"Arcane Anathema","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your curse is disruptive to other forms of magic. As an action, you can touch a creature and attempt to free it from a spell’s effects. Make a curse ability check against a DC equal to 10 + twice the spell’s level. On a success, you end the effects of the spell on the target. This has no effect on any of the spell’s other targets.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/symbols/ring-circle-smoke-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.D8SaLt4gfBmwgOqG"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674804693805,"modifiedTime":1674808148240,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"zOqEwSUxQtD9oy1u"}
{"name":"Hex Shield","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.77C0G2CtkzJ8oGrV]{Hex Aura} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.QO1BqfrqMdwY0aMx]{Hex Plate}</p><p>You can concentrate your curse’s magicks to deflect weapons and magic. Whenever you take damage, you can use your reaction to halve the amount of damage you take.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-teal.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.J00N4BJLGJFPRxHK"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674811783989,"modifiedTime":1674813227822,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"zjiZRmfOFiI2X1I4"}
{"name":"Umbral Imprecation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Prerequisite: 18th level, @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.0tBZAWioRXe0Blk0]{Muffling Imprecation} or @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.5xStL1jkpH0s5uYm]{Sleighting Imprecation}</p><p>If you don’t already have darkvision, you gain darkvision to a range of 60 feet. Magical darkness doesn’t impede your darkvision.</p><p>Additionally, your curse creates a shadowy gloom around you. While in an area of bright light, you count as being in dim light; while in an area of dim light, you count as being in darkness; and while in an area of darkness, you count as being in magical darkness.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Accursed","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/eyes/humanoid-single-yellow.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.sQR601nF3eIbVA6y"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674812494580,"modifiedTime":1674813283494,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"zkwQX3Ii00Biv2se"}
